  std_ec1w_tip_fw_corner: 'Length of a wall return at the corner (an L-shaped or U-shaped plan). A return corner reduces c_p,net in zones A and B per EN 1991-1-4 §7.4.1 Note 2. Set to 0 for a plain wall with no return.',
  std_ec1w_tip_fw_phi: 'Ratio of solid area to total (enclosed) area of the wall. φ=1.0 for a fully solid wall. For open/porous walls (fences, lattice), φ < 1.0 and c_p,net is reduced by φ. See EN 1991-1-4 §7.4.1(3).',
