  std_ec1w_tip_ws_b: 'The horizontal width of the sign face. Defines the reference area A_ref = b × h. Also used to compute horizontal eccentricity: e = ±0.25 b from the geometric centre. See EN 1991-1-4 §7.4.3(2).',
